    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>How to Contact Children's Music Program</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>David Weinstone letter on July 9 article on children's song classes at Musical Theater Works in Manhattan offers his e-mail address and phone number (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>I would like to add a postscript to your article ''Songs for Children That Won't Make the Adults Fwow Up'' (July 9). If people want information on my classes, called ''Music for Aardvarks and Other Mammals,'' or want to buy tapes, they may call (718) 858-1741 or send e-mail to tang404@hotmail.com. The classes are held at Musical Theater Works at 440 Lafayette Street in Lower Manhattan.</p>
        <p>DAVID WEINSTONE  Carroll Gardens, Brooklyn</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
